Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.05,0:00:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两舷减速前进 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维持既定高度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推进系统 地球航行模式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.50,0:00:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.42,0:00:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 索敌系统没有报警
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周边未发现高危目标
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.99,0:00:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰当前 正取道这条航线
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向失落楼兰移动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.51,0:00:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预计两天后抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据称各部队正在当地集结
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.17,0:00:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为向它发动总攻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.65,0:00:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我们抵达基地后也将参战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.87,0:00:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么不慌不忙地行进 没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.60,0:00:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.96,0:00:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不… 我是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.66,0:00:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果飞得更高 速度更快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.02,0:00:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用一天就可以到达
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:01:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为避免被轨道上空的敌人发现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过计算敌人的轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拟定的最佳航线和速度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的行动一旦被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.32,0:01:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅殃及失落楼兰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.18,0:01:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战目的也会暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.50,0:01:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.82,0:01:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 关于抵达后的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.47,0:01:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.30,0:01:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.38,0:01:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰底发生爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量红外线反应
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.68,0:01:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人袭击！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星移民计划
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因其失败被遗留在火星圈的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.39,0:01:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自称独立国家维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向地球联邦政府宣战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.91,0:02:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争开始 已将近70年
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到从砂中发动突袭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂中移动的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过影像分析发现有18台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时有微弱的电子干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初步认定为集团作战的无人机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外暂无发现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪找不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候真佩服维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开发出这么适应地球环境的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想没用的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这确实值得深思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他们拥有比联邦先进的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以隐身衣为代表的高科技又是从何而来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这神秘感令人欲罢不能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在重在想方设法应对敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管侥幸逃过一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神号却付出推进系统受损的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动能力下降
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有件事让我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有机动战士出现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻影3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚看到新来的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维甘武装暴动当时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里附近航行的联邦战舰与敌人遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.19,0:05:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其后失去联系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.07,0:05:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽曾派救援部队前往
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后者亦下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据遇敌战舰最后的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人是三台机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总计两艘战舰和十台机动战士被毁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总部将其归类为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真身不明的敌人部队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自那以后称为「幻影3」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻影3…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙漠的亡灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这情报为什么现在才来？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.09,0:05:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 别动气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 现在清楚一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人肯定会卷土重来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以必须用尽能用的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.44,0:05:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 所有机动战士更换成沙漠型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其次…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷他们在谈什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在那里干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.39,0:06:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤诺亚姑姑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？你在这艘船上做卫生员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫星上接到的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忙这忙那的没来得及告诉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到能和姑姑乘上同一艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很高兴能和爸爸还有你在同艘船上工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 罗玛丽和妈妈有消息了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是在附近城市里避难
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧也该和她们联系一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗玛丽一定会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了 无非就是叫我下船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做父母的都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗 快逃 哈罗 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让它逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:06:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 听见没！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 吉欧 尤诺亚老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难为你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.43,0:07:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这身打扮是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 现在忙不过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等会跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温蒂不是学过医疗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她在我身边帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一份工作就是照顾孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原来这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.39,0:07:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原来在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜路亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长叫我指导你 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伍德比特 接下来是这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 刚来就这么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 能亲眼见识洛蒂师傅的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉提高特别大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.92,0:07:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 错了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说几遍才记住？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.57,0:08:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看模拟战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被训得挺惨的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧跟你年龄相仿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又都是新人 要好好相处哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.83,0:08:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 动手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住 时刻保持移动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌握敌人位置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火后也不能放松警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住这三点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然要我这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且和爷爷教的不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太过重视攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简而言之就是太冒进
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在教你怎么干掉对手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.61,0:08:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是在战场求生的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 只守不攻没法取胜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是爷爷的教诲？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果死了还谈什么胜负？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住战斗不只是冲锋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:09:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 休息几分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷摸摸躲在那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来还需要一阵子才能修完
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说 队长？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就给它个下马威吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不急
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等摸清自动炮台的部署 它想逃也难
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好 在做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.06,0:09:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我们在检查它的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE构筑器？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 刚输入高达迄今为止的战斗记录
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是菲利特先生吩咐的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看能不能造出沙漠战需要的装备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然见过一面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但像这样正式问候还是第一次吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫洛蒂·麦德纳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船的工程主管
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢那套MS对战模拟系统吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…这么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…和这位伍德比特跟明日野家有点缘分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我修过几次你爸的高达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的爷爷是菲利特先生的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的妈妈和你的爸爸还是同一个部队的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 不愧是英雄的孙子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年纪轻轻驾驶高达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还那么能打 了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛蒂先生 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是叫伍德比特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫吉欧·明日野 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少得意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有得意…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么明日野家族
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.51,0:10:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算你爷爷是联邦军老司令 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:10:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶过高达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.47,0:10:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当自己有多了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛蒂师傅他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.21,0:11:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是著名的麦德纳工坊的继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.25,0:11:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他主动参军 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一介士兵做到工程主管
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.59,0:11:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论决心还是志向 你都没法和他比！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没资格跟他这么说话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来 你崇拜洛蒂先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很崇拜爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真的很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 伍德比特君 想见见爷爷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能学到不少东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有完没完啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为所有人都会给你特殊待遇
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.10,0:11:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他为什么那么生气？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.79,0:12:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 吉欧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比休息前状态的还差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷真的是个很了不起的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.34,0:12:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伍德比特如果了解爷爷的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.24,0:12:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实谁也不想看到你这样的孩子上战场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜路亚小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论有多严厉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.36,0:12:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是想你在战斗中生还
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.13,0:12:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.18,0:12:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 这话从何说起？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是情绪低落？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 只是分心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.34,0:12:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样比较容易让孩子安心 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 是我误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执行岗哨任务的乔纳森机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在砂中发现移动物体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数量3
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待命中的机师请准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(640,666)}（来了!）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达的新部件如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解析完成 但还在构筑中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.39,0:13:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离完成还要一定时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.97,0:13:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有赶上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得已了 用AGE-3出击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.63,0:13:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狩猎时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯队 按准备会的部署行动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和乔纳森 德雷克在上空吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜路亚和奥布莱特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锁定无人机位置后攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍利奇·阿比斯 Cnanche-CUSTAM
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.25,0:13:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不可以飞？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知敌人藏在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.34,0:14:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样只会变成活靶子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍利奇他们已经去承担这份职责
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你专心摧毁无人机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙漠型也显得行动缓慢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.82,0:14:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧·明日野 高达出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心 机体容易陷入砂里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宁愿放慢动作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要保持机体平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.85,0:14:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了 是高达
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极品猎物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包围它！痛扁它！歼灭它！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么东西来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.04,0:15:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三角洲·攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 下沉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.57,0:16:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.48,0:16:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.52,0:16:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.61,0:16:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特先生 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新武器 G-Hopper
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 立即发射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行空中换装
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.36,0:16:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中换装…机师呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.98,0:16:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛蒂师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是开动它的话 我也没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那让我去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维修班不能没有洛蒂师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.01,0:16:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.95,0:16:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伍德比特！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他随随便便就能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定也能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别紧张 细节交给自动驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伍德比特·甘海尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G-Hopper 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.37,0:17:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管它呢 打下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.12,0:17:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧 空中换装！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为我们会看着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:17:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:17:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 快完成合体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是AGE-3 FORTRESS（要塞）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.29,0:18:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.03,0:18:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住这3点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想逃？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次三角洲攻击送他归天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:18:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持运动为的是不被敌人瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.41,0:19:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死 到处乱窜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耍小聪明的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时刻掌握敌人位置的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既容易躲避攻击 也容易反击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.12,0:19:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.58,0:19:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火以后也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不放松警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴蒙！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧 老夫果然没看错你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷 大家 快躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.14,0:20:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伍德比特君？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伍德比特…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那么客气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我伍德比特就可以了 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:21:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安息吧 兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.09,0:21:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定为你报这个仇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.23,0:21:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜路亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉了一台幻影3
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.19,0:21:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜路亚小姐教我的 真的很管用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.29,0:21:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台被击落的机动战士里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是人在驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.31,0:21:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可他们是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人也有家人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.72,0:21:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争不是什么值得高兴的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.50,0:21:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜路亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.32,0:21:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜路亚很少说起自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.28,0:21:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在战争中失去了父母
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.03,0:21:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说妹妹也重病缠身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.14,0:21:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我却在她面前…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.94,0:22:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次次为敌人伤心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.44,0:22:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人会疯的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.20,0:22:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为胜利高兴并没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.92,0:22:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
